\c 36
\s Umlayo omayelana lokwenda kwendlalifa zesifazana
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusondela inhloko zaboyise zensendo zabantwana bakoGileyadi indodana kaMakiri indodana kaManase\x + 26.29.\x*, abosendo lwabantwana bakoJosefa, zakhuluma phambi kukaMozisi laphambi kweziphathamandla, inhloko zaboyise babantwana bakoIsrayeli,
\v 2 zathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* yalaya inkosi yami ukuthi iphe abantwana bakoIsrayeli ilizwe njengelifa ngenkatho\x + 26.55. 33.54.\x*; futhi inkosi yami yalaywa yiN\nd kosi\nd* ukuthi inike ilifa likaZelofehadi umfowethu kumadodakazi akhe\x + 27.1. Josh. 17.3,4.\x*.
\v 3 Uba esendela kwenye yamadodana ezizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli, ilifa lawo lizasuswa elifeni labobaba\x + 27.4.\x*, lengezelelwe elifeni lalesosizwe azakuba ngawaso; ngalokho lizasuswa kunkatho yelifa lethu\x + 27.4.\x*.
\v 4 Lalapho kuzakuba \w lijubili\w** labantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Levi 25.10.\x*, ilifa lawo lizakwengezelelwa elifeni lalesosizwe azakuba ngawaso; ngalokho ilifa lawo lizasuswa elifeni lesizwe sabobaba\x + 27.4.\x*.
\v 5 UMozisi waselaya abantwana bakoIsrayeli ngokomlomo weN\nd kosi\nd* esithi: Isizwe sabantwana bakoJosefa sikhulume kuhle\x + 27.7.\x*.
\v 6 Le yinto iN\nd kosi\nd* eyilayileyo mayelana lamadodakazi kaZelofehadi isithi: Kawendele kulabo abahle emehlweni awo, kodwa kawendele osendweni lwesizwe sikayise\x + 36.12.\x*.
\v 7 Ngalokho ilifa labantwana bakoIsrayeli kalingabhodi lisuke esizweni liye esizweni, ngoba abantwana bakoIsrayeli bazanamathela, ngulowo lalowo elifeni lesizwe saboyise\x + 1 Kho. 21.3.\x*.
\v 8 Layileyo laleyo indodakazi edla ilifa esizweni sabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 1 Lan. 23.22.\x* izakwendela komunye wosendo wesizwe sikayise, ukuze abantwana bakoIsrayeli badle ilifa, omunye lomunye ilifa laboyise.
\v 9 Ngalokho ilifa kaliyikubhoda lisuke esizweni liye kwesinye isizwe, ngoba izizwe zabantwana bakoIsrayeli zizanamathela, ngulowo lalowo elifeni lakhe.
\v 10 Njengokulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuMozisi enza njalo amadodakazi kaZelofehadi;
\v 11 ngoba uMahla, uTiriza, loHogila, loMilka, loNowa, amadodakazi kaZelofehadi, endela emadodaneni abafowabo bakayise\x + 27.1.\x*.
\v 12 Endela kunsendo zabantwana bakoManase indodana kaJosefa, lelifa lawo lahlala esizweni sosendo lukayise.
\v 13 Le yimilayo lezahlulelo iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazilaya abantwana bakoIsrayeli ngesandla sikaMozisi emagcekeni akoMowabi eJordani eJeriko\x + 22.1.\x*.